data.description: Welcome to 1048 E Lewis Street, a delightful craftsman-style home conveniently nestled near schools, parks, bus stops, and the university. The cozy covered porch sets the stage for a warm welcome. Inside, you'll find a cozy living room adorned with beautiful wood floors, exuding character and comfort. The heart of the home, the kitchen, features a spacious pantry and is perfectly positioned for convenience and functionality. Two generously proportioned bedrooms and a full bathroom on the main floor ensure comfortable living spaces for you and your family. As you venture downstairs, the unfinished basement beckons with untapped potential, offering the opportunity to expand and tailor your living space to your exact needs. Outside, the backyard beckons with a generous patio, providing an ideal spot for outdoor gatherings and relaxation. Fully fenced, it offers both privacy and security for your enjoyment.
